{"tid":541044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大天體碩士生肉搏新紮師姐","createTime":"2018-01-26T04:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T05:02:50.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13c2f0a65c8bcc314f25a0009ffd4f06b5aff524","tid":541044,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"勇警花街頭大戰「天體碩士生」。一名男子昨晨在繁忙時間脫光衣服，衝出北角英皇道穿梭車群赤裸狂奔，又大字形瞓地阻路及圖強闖電車，新紮佗槍師姐首先趕至，與男子「裸聊」時，被推跌地上受傷，急忙拔出伸縮警棍與裸男正面交鋒，多次發生推扯，有人疑深知闖禍，瞓地及「三叩首」求饒，雙方對峙近三分鐘，增援警員到場與師姐將裸男制服，他涉襲警被捕，與受傷師姐一併送院。裸男送院時聲稱：「我喺浸大讀碩士，嚟香港讀書壓力好大&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"19a08360c1afa77f9fdae01e4d4c95457a6ca7a1","tid":541044,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"83ca10e2a9d198ff4e73ec1eafa9a32fc8aad2bc","tid":541044,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"威過中大碩士<br />\n<br />\n點解唔叫雞"},{"pid":"fa5c7a0d849592ba91ad79cbfef3e4bb7f4a50ce","tid":541044,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20131203/00405_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20131203%2F00405_001.html&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4759314a\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20131203/00405_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2013年12月3日 (二)</span></strong></span>"}]}